]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wayde van Niekerkis a household name in South Africa.\", \"from\": 380, \"to\": 433, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 420, \"end\": 432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999998772182, \"rank\": 1.2285523576334496e-10, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has been ever since winning the Olympic 400m gold in world-record time atRio 2016.\", \"from\": 434, \"to\": 519, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Running in lane eight, Van Niekerk crossed the line in 43.03 seconds, claiming a world record previously held since 1999 by the sport's greatMichael Johnson.\", \"from\": 520, \"to\": 677, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 669, \"end\": 676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\", \"score\": 0.6069010122837932, \"rank\": 0.6423683435550054, \"text\": \"Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Increasingly, there appear to be positive signs of Van Niekerk rediscovering his best form after an injury-plagued period in his career, which began with a freak accident in 2017 when he he tore his anterior cruciate ligament and meniscus cartilage during a charity touch rugby match at Newlands.\", \"from\": 679, \"to\": 975, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 966, \"end\": 974, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newlands_Stadium\", \"score\": 0.9842563428480111, \"rank\": 0.01599548457717234, \"text\": \"Newlands\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newlands_Stadium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newlands_Stadium\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hopefully that isall behind him, though, as he recently posted an Olympic qualifying time of 44.08 seconds at the 2023 Silesia Diamond League meeting in Poland.\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 1137, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1096, \"end\": 1103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Silesia\", \"score\": 0.9960854445478515, \"rank\": 0.003915377268716698, \"text\": \"Silesia\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Silesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Silesia\"}, {\"begin\": 1104, \"end\": 1118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0936931537128247e-13, \"text\": \"Diamond League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\"}, {\"begin\": 1130, \"end\": 1136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9205882595614981, \"rank\": 0.08624795464584398, \"text\": \"Poland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If we think of any athlete who had a crazy, unexpected injury, most likely do not make finals and do not challenge for races,\\\" Van Niekerk said on theBehind the Ruck Podcast.\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1314, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is about being kinder with yourself again, allowing yourself to be exposed to that environment again, and start believing you are a champion again.\\\"\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1467, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just a few days ago, Van Niekerk, Gardeo Isaacs, Zakithi Nene and Lythe Pillaybooked their ticketto the Paris Olympics when they ended second in their heat at the World Relays in Bahamas.\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1656, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1526, \"end\": 1530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/River_Nene\", \"score\": 0.99999997464